text: Jean-Lou Paiani (born 13 December 1988 in Sallanches) is a French cyclist from Megève, Rhône-Alpes, France. ==Palmares== ;2009 : 1st Stage 2 Tour de l'Avenir : 1st Stage 2 Tour Nivernais Morvan : 6th Paris–Roubaix Espoirs ;2012 : 2nd Grand Prix de la Ville de Lillers ;2014 : 1st Stage 1 Paris-Arras Tour (TTT) ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:French male cyclists Category:Université Savoie-Mont Blanc alumni
title: Jean-Lou Paiani
